snippet.textDisplay: Two things.  One: that vet is in helluva good shape for his age.  That prat fall was half fake and half real (because flat on the ground was the safest place to be as the enormity of his good fortune hit home).  But to be able to go down on the asphalt and then spring back up like that is something a lot of people 20 years his junior would have a hard time doing.  Two: he seems like a decent and humble guy who absolutely deserves whatever happiness and good fortune this watch brings to him.  Given his service to country  and what sure sounded like a strong moral compass, he's absolutely earned this unexpected good fortune.
